By Andile Mngxitama If you missed the debate yesterday (17 May 2020) at 20:00 on the possible influences that my essay Blacks Can’t Be Racist (BCBR) has had on the Rhodes Must Fall (RMF)/Fees Must Fall (FMF) moments, you can now get it on YouTube. The debate features great insights from the fallists Kamvelihle Goba; Simthandile Tyhali; Masixole Mlandu; and Thobani Zikalala; as well as myself. Watch the YouTube video: https://youtu.be/9hsfefP–Hg Order your copy of the 10th Anniversary edition of BCBR via WhatsApp, email or go to the Facebook page, Blacks Can’t Be Racist Andile Mngxitama is the President of Black First Land First (BLF), a radical black consciousness organization.